air quote \u2014 no jargon, no pressure.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>2 \u00b7 Design &amp; build</h3><p>We design and build your site, branded to you, fast and search-ready, keeping you in the loop throughout.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>3 \u00b7 Launch &amp; grow</h3><p>We launch, host and optimise your site \u2014 then keep supporting you as your business grows.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "85d7a14", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "4ab598a", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Common Questions</span>\n<h2>Web design &amp; SEO FAQs</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container faq\">\n<details open=\"\"><summary>How much does a small business website cost?</summary><p>Every project is quoted individually, but we keep our prices genuinely low and fair \u2014 most small-business sites cost far less than people expect. Tell us what you need on the <a href=\"/web-seo-enquiry/\">enquiry form</a> and we'll send a clear, no-pressure quote.</p></details>\n<details><summary>Do you offer SEO as well as web design?</summary><p>Yes. Every site is built search-ready with clean code, fast loading, structured data and on-page SEO. We can also set up local search so the right customers find you on Google.</p></details>\n<details><summary>Are you a Manchester-based web designer?</summary><p>Yes \u2014 we're based in Manchester and work with small businesses across Greater Manchester, Chesh